relation: Wha?? Where'd these lightsabers come from!?
I'm no Mandalorian... I'm a Sithalorian and proud of it!!
If only this blue saber were green, then I could direct traffic. My lifelong dream!
Bounty hunting having taken a turn for the worse, our hero is forced to accept a job guiding in aircraft at the Endor International Airport.
Yeah, that's right... I killed Darth Vader AND Luke Skywalker. Now I have unlimited power!
Lightsabers... Ewok village... THIS MUST BE A NIGHTMARE!!!
By the power of Grayskull ... er ... Jedi ... Sith? I am Boba Fett!
Boba Fett now comes with a double order of pure awesomeness. Get yours today.
Say hello to my little friends!
"Yeah you know this is the most awesomist thing I've ever done."
Wait a second...... where did THESE come from?!
Back from the DEAD!!! Also guess what? Boba got him self a Lightsaber make that two!
All work and no play makes Boba a dull boy!!
Oh, damn! I didn't know I was a Jedi..... or a Sith.....?

I killed them. I killed them all. They're dead, every single one of them. And not just the men... but the women, and the children too. They're like animals! And I slaughtered them like animals! I hate ewoks!
"I'm here to kick ass and take names! In fact, forget the names!"
Don't know where THESE came from, but I guess you'll never see the light of day, my little Ewok friends!
Look at me now Jedi!! Take that ... Eat your heart out Jedi!! I can do this double time!
HA!!! you all thought Darth Vader Luke Skywalker ,,were the holders of this Laser Swords Boba Fett is the Man
um... I have no idea how I got these...... DIE EWOKS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
GET OFF MY LAWN YOU CRAZY KIDS!!
look at this new trick I learned
This year i get to carve the ewok!
Red for the right hand, blue for the left hand. Or was it the other way around??
There's no need to run guys--I just wanted to show you my new FX lightsabers!
Ya'll bout to get pwned by da FETT MAN!

"You take the blue lightsaber, the story ends, you wake up dead and believe whatever you want to believe. You take the red lightsaber, you stay in Wonderland, and I show you how deep the rabbit hole goes."
You've just entered...the Twilight zone *Twilight Zone Theme*
I am the icon for the 'Republic Of Alsace-Lorraine'; France and Germany had better not mess with me! I will strike down the Frenchman on my left and the German on my right!
*hears Boba Fett sing* I'M TOO SEXY FOR MY 'SABERS TOO SEXY FOR MY SABERS TOO SEXY YEAHHHH!! *watches Boba wiggle his hips in sync with the music....*
Does it come in green too?
oh yeah,what you gonna do now
Boba was tripping balls at the ewok rave.
